    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3007660/extras/a6555f098699452ef5a7e986dc1bc481.avif?t=1729502151\" width=622 height=254 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >贝拉想玩！你陪贝拉玩！</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你被困在了贝拉的世界。在这个世界里，贝拉是神一般的存在。贝拉想让你陪它一起玩，并为它提供血液。放置血道和可以造成伤害的魔体来消灭贝拉的各位朋友及其奇形怪状的仆从。只是不要让它们抵达你的迷宫尽头，否则贝拉就会生气。贝拉一旦生气，就会永远把你困在这里。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >美味的策略！</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >选择你的路径，挑选特定的奖励而要面对的怪物。决定你要寻找血道、魔体，而是可以用来升级技能的强力加成。每次流程都不一样，你永远不会玩到两次一模一样的游戏。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3007660/extras/ccf0ea47772f4369adb30f2b9d535056.poster.avif?t=1729502151\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3007660/extras/ccf0ea47772f4369adb30f2b9d535056.webm?t=1729502151\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3007660/extras/ccf0ea47772f4369adb30f2b9d535056.mp4?t=1729502151\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >可口的选择！</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >怪物们会在你铺设的血道的另一头出生。你是想用精心放置的魔体构建蜿蜒曲折的血道，还是构建短小精悍的夹击通道？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >诱人的奖励！</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在打败贝拉的怪物朋友们的同时，解锁强大的新怪物、魔体和加成。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >充分利用手头的资源，在贝拉的游戏中生存下来。它也许会放你离开。也许。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
